WEBVTT

00:03:29.028 --> 00:03:31.241
from looking upon him,

00:03:31.265 --> 00:03:36.011
for fear that would be
the lasting image of him in her mind.

00:03:37.392 --> 00:03:40.635
But you know who we would see
again and again?

00:03:40.659 --> 00:03:42.027
The murderer.

00:03:42.476 --> 00:03:45.567
His pictures were everywhere.

00:03:46.796 --> 00:03:50.160
One article was six paragraphs long

00:03:51.674 --> 00:03:56.569
and featured his name 41 times.

00:03:57.427 --> 00:04:00.664
The media had made him famous.